Oh, my... my baby... Oh, my baby, you're alive.

1159
01:28:37,559 --> 01:28:39,595
你活着。
You're alive.

1160
01:28:39,729 --> 01:28:40,963
我很爱你。
I love you so much.

1161
01:28:42,832 --> 01:28:47,502
