1165
01:28:54,476 --> 01:28:56,746
你开始明白了。
You're beginning to catch on.

1166
01:29:10,159 --> 01:29:11,761
这是一个奇迹!
It's a miracle!

1167
01:29:23,306 --> 01:29:26,943
