He just told me what to do and... I did it.

1176
01:30:14,790 --> 01:30:18,327
真相是……你们都能治好人。
The truth is... all of you can cure people.

1177
01:30:18,461 --> 01:30:21,330
你真的可以。
You really can.

1178
01:30:21,464 --> 01:30:28,371
你所要做的就是相信上帝并向他祈祷，他会帮助你的。
All you have to do is believe in God and pray to Him, and He'll help you.

1179
01:30:28,536 --> 01:30:31,974
