Sometimes... we can't see it right away.

1180
01:30:32,108 --> 01:30:39,415
或者有时候答案并不是你所祈祷的，但是……他的听力。
Or sometimes the answer isn't exactly what you've prayed for, but... He's listening.

1181
01:30:39,547 --> 01:30:44,186
很快你就会看到他是多么的仁慈和奇妙。
And soon you'll see how kind and how wonderful He is.

1182
01:30:44,320 --> 01:30:46,521
他是最好的。
He's the best.

1183
01:30:49,658 --> 01:31:02,204
他让我告诉你………爱你的孩子和你的家庭，并且试着每天互相帮助。
He told me to tell you... to... love your children and your families, and to try to help one another every day.

1184
01:31:04,539 --> 01:31:15,418
